## Scope

This file is loaded automatically by Claude Code when the working directory is
**anywhere inside `backend/`**. It replaces the root `CLAUDE.md` for the
purposes of standards injection and agent routing for all Rust work.

Cross-cutting concerns (git workflow, commit conventions, root routing) remain
governed by the root `CLAUDE.md`. When in doubt, the root CLAUDE.md takes
precedence on cross-layer decisions; this file takes precedence on
Rust-specific implementation choices.

