## DO NOT Load

The following standards are **explicitly excluded** when inside `backend/`:

- `flutter/*` — Flutter concerns belong in `frontend/`.
- `infra/*` — Infrastructure concerns are owned by `infra/` and Atlas.
- `global/proto-contracts` — Proto contract governance is a Hermes-API /
  cross-layer concern; changes to `shared/protos/` must be routed through the
  root CLAUDE.md and Janus.

