## Testing Requirements

| Scope                          | Coverage Target | Tools                           |
|--------------------------------|-----------------|---------------------------------|
| `crates/domain/`               | 100%            | cargo test, proptest            |
| `crates/application/`          | 100%            | cargo test, mockall, proptest   |
| `crates/grpc-api/`             | ≥ 80%           | cargo test, tonic test helpers  |
| `crates/infrastructure/`       | ≥ 80%           | cargo test, testcontainers-rs   |
| `bin-server/`                  | smoke tests only| cargo test (integration)        |
| **Overall workspace**          | **≥ 80%**       | cargo-tarpaulin or cargo-llvm-cov |

- **BDD scenarios**: Use `cucumber-rs` for user-facing behaviors. Feature
  files live in `tests/features/`.
- **Property tests**: Use `proptest` for domain invariants (value object
  constraints, aggregate business rules).
- **Port fakes**: Use `mockall` to generate mock implementations of port
  traits for application-layer unit tests.

---

## Cross-Layer Concerns

| Concern                    | Action required                                               |
|----------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------|
| Proto changes              | Edit `shared/protos/` only — notify Hermes-API; regenerate stubs via `tonic-build` in `crates/grpc-api/build.rs` |
| Frontend API changes       | Route through root CLAUDE.md + Janus (cross-layer agent)      |
| Infra changes (DB schema)  | Coordinate with Atlas; migrations live in `infra/`            |
| Observability config       | Sentinel handles OTLP exporter wiring in `bin-server/main.rs` |

